nodes.text: The Nebular Kelpie was a modified Lancer-class pursuit craft owned by the Shungbeek Kid Malmash.
During the war between the First Order and the Resistance, Malmash used the starship to transport refugees to safe locations.
In 35 ABY, the Nebular Kelpie part of a fleet assembled by Lando Calrissian to assist the Resistance during the battle against the Sith Eternal forces over the planet Exegol.
